🌽 Maize has become a staple food in many parts of the world, with total production surpassing that of wheat or rice. However not all of this maize is consumed directly by humans. What are you having for breakfast?! I bet you didn't have a something that met all your nutritional needs. I sure didn't. These "Milk Fed" veal calves have a milk replacer specially designed to fit their nutrional needs which includes plenty of protein. Contrary to popular belief veal calves health is very important. Their iron is monitored via blood tests to ensure they have enough iron and are NOT anemic. A well balanced diet of milk replacer and grain ensures this. 
If you have any questions, let me know! My brain is on information overload.
